Permission is hereby granted to any individual or organization to use, copy, modify, and distribute the Software in source code or binary form, subject to the following conditions:

1. Redistributions of source code must retain the above copyright notice and this entire license text without modification.  
2. The Software may not be relicensed under different terms by any party.  
3. Use of the Software by any for-profit organization with fifty (50) or more employees worldwide requires a commercial license under Section 3, regardless of how the Software was obtained.  
4. Registered nonprofit organizations and accredited educational institutions are exempt from this requirement and may use the Software under Section 2 regardless of employee count.  
5. Contractors and individual contributors do not count as employees for the purposes of this license.  

