### Section 3: Commercial Terms (for for-profit organizations with 50 or more employees worldwide)

Any for-profit company, corporation, or organization with fifty (50) or more employees worldwide must purchase a commercial license for use of FlutterBluePlus, subject to the Common Conditions and the following additional terms:

1. The cost of the commercial license is $2999 USD.  
2. The license grants perpetual rights to use the Software as it exists at the time of purchase.  
3. The license also entitles the licensee to updates and bug fixes for a period of three hundred sixty-five (365) days from the date of purchase.  
4. Continued access to updates beyond this period requires purchasing a new commercial license.  
5. Payment must be made via the official payment portal: https://jamcorder.myshopify.com/products/flutterblueplus-commercial-license


A valid commercial license covers use of all current and future packages that
are part of the FlutterBluePlus project, including its federated packages
(e.g., flutter_blue_plus, flutter_blue_plus_darwin, flutter_blue_plus_android,
flutter_blue_plus_web, flutter_blue_plus_linux, flutter_blue_plus_platform_interface). 
Only a single commercial license is required per organization, regardless of how many
FlutterBluePlus packages are used.

